Universitas Pelita Harapan Conference for Student Government Leaders (UPH CSGL) 2016 is an event held by BEM-UPH with support from the Rectorates, Student Life, and MPM UPH in mission to gather the leaders of student organizations as the voice of change. A pioneering event, UPH CSGL will bring change to UPH's student body, as new policies and collective agreement among all student government leaders will be re-created for the better good. 
This act is held in hope for a much better cooperation between student organizations, thus bringing unity and solidarity through discussion and communication forums which will be held throughout the event. 
The act of unity, once and for all, will be held on Saturday, 19th of November 2016 at D502, 07.15 am. 
Calling for all student government leaders, to gather and be an agent of change. 
From this day on, may the change for the better begin! 
#bem_uph #spiritofexcellence #uphcsgl2016
